rs in a complex environment and focus on the delivery of results in the form of engagement, leads and sales - English language native level - marketing experience: familiar with marketing procedures and being able to create a strategy - working in a European timezone good knowledge of the crypto space and being able to understand its dynamics - at least basic financial background Skills Marketing Compensation tbd Applications for this job are currently closed. ", 
